00:11:26,519 --> 00:11:29,688
<font color="japanese">化け物の正体が
<font color="japanese">韮崎理子だと分かった時の

194
00:11:30,231 --> 00:11:33,067
<font color="japanese">あんたの怯え方は
<font color="japanese">尋常じゃなかったからな

195
00:11:35,611 --> 00:11:39,281
<font color="japanese">ええ　理子さんも私も覚醒し

196
00:11:39,782 --> 00:11:42,201
<font color="japanese">佐々木学園に入学しました

197
00:11:43,244 --> 00:11:45,246
<font color="japanese">学園が封鎖された時

198
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:46,747
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生に

199
00:11:46,831 --> 00:11:49,333
<font color="japanese">ミュータント研究の
<font color="japanese">助手を頼まれ

200
00:11:49,834 --> 00:11:54,338
<font color="japanese">それ以来ずっと 理子さんと
<font color="japanese">一緒に働いてきたんです

201
00:11:54,422 --> 00:11:55,756
<font color="japanese">うっ…

202
00:11:56,215 --> 00:11:58,968
<font color="japanese">その理子さんが
<font color="japanese">あんなことに…

203
00:11:59,468 --> 00:12:01,095
<font color="japanese">うっ　う…

204
00:12:02,012 --> 00:12:03,931
<font color="japanese">何を注射していたんだ？

205
00:12:04,598 --> 00:12:05,933
<font color="japanese">それは…

206
00:12:06,016 --> 00:12:07,852
<font color="japanese">韮崎理子も打っていたが

207
00:12:08,561 --> 00:12:10,354
<font color="japanese">言えないほど
<font color="japanese">やばいものなのか？

208
00:12:12,064 --> 00:12:16,235
<font color="japanese">先生の許しがなければ
<font color="japanese">私の口からは…

209
00:12:16,902 --> 00:12:18,028
<font color="japanese">そうか

210
00:12:18,112 --> 00:12:20,614
<font color="japanese">佐々木結衣に言われて
<font color="japanese">黙っているんだな

211
00:12:21,949 --> 00:12:24,535
<font color="japanese">真田 純もミュータントか？

212
00:12:25,035 --> 00:12:26,120
<font color="japanese">そうです

213
00:12:26,662 --> 00:12:28,122
<font color="japanese">彼も佐々木学園に？

214
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:33,461
<font color="japanese">いえ 彼はここに来て半年も
<font color="japanese">経っていません

215
00:12:34,128 --> 00:12:36,464
<font color="japanese">優秀な研究員だからと

216
00:12:36,547 --> 00:12:38,883
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生が
<font color="japanese">連れてきたんです

217
00:12:39,842 --> 00:12:41,844
<font color="japanese">ほんとに４人だけなのか

218
00:12:42,344 --> 00:12:44,138
<font color="japanese">この研究所にいるのは？

219
00:12:44,221 --> 00:12:45,139
<font color="japanese">ええ

220
00:12:46,223 --> 00:12:49,059
<font color="japanese">とにかく 今すぐビーストに

221
00:12:49,143 --> 00:12:52,313
<font color="japanese">エグゼビアー機関で開発した
<font color="japanese">ワクチンを打ってもらえ

222
00:12:53,272 --> 00:12:56,025
<font color="japanese">でも… 先生が何と言うか…

223
00:12:56,650 --> 00:12:58,486
<font color="japanese">また先生かよ

224
00:12:59,069 --> 00:13:02,114
<font color="japanese">先生のこと
<font color="japanese">信頼しているんです

225
00:13:02,198 --> 00:13:03,908
<font color="japanese">ふん！ やれやれ…

226
00:13:03,991 --> 00:13:07,661
<font color="japanese">グッ… ググ… ううっ

227
00:13:08,454 --> 00:13:11,081
<font color="japanese">それにしても
<font color="japanese">なぜなんだろうね？

228
00:13:11,165 --> 00:13:11,707
<font color="japanese">え？

229
00:13:11,790 --> 00:13:14,585
<font color="japanese">この地方には 多くの
<font color="japanese">ミュータントがいるのに

230
00:13:15,085 --> 00:13:18,005
<font color="japanese">セレブロには
<font color="japanese">ミュータント反応がなかった

231
00:13:18,088 --> 00:13:21,091
<font color="japanese">しかも
<font color="japanese">佐々木家のあるこの一帯では

232
00:13:21,592 --> 00:13:24,553
<font color="japanese">デイモン･ホール症候群を
<font color="japanese">発症したミュータントが

233
00:13:24,637 --> 00:13:25,679
<font color="japanese">何人かいる

234
00:13:26,722 --> 00:13:27,848
<font color="japanese">そうなの？

235
00:13:28,724 --> 00:13:29,934
<font color="japanese">知らなかったわ

236
00:13:31,227 --> 00:13:32,561
<font color="japanese">ほんとよ

237
00:13:33,604 --> 00:13:35,940
<font color="japanese">そのような報告は
<font color="japanese">何も受けてなかったし…

238
00:13:36,023 --> 00:13:38,943
<font color="japanese">ミュータントと医療について
<font color="japanese">研究している者が

239
00:13:40,569 --> 00:13:43,906
<font color="japanese">知らないでは済まされないと
<font color="japanese">思うんだがな

240
00:13:45,991 --> 00:13:47,701
<font color="japanese">彼女のこともそうだ

241
00:13:48,661 --> 00:13:51,288
<font color="japanese">最初からミュータントだと
<font color="japanese">知らされていれば

242
00:13:51,372 --> 00:13:53,749
<font color="japanese">こんなことにはならなくて
<font color="japanese">済んだのに…

243
00:13:55,209 --> 00:13:58,087
<font color="japanese">まさか理子さんが
<font color="japanese">こうなってしまうなんて

244
00:13:58,587 --> 00:14:00,506
<font color="japanese">考えてもみなかったわ

245
00:14:01,006 --> 00:14:02,466
<font color="japanese">んっ… う…

246
00:14:03,425 --> 00:14:04,635
<font color="japanese">ごめんなさい

247
00:14:05,135 --> 00:14:06,720
<font color="japanese">気分がすぐれないの

248
00:14:07,805 --> 00:14:09,932
<font color="japanese">少し休ませてもらうわ

249
00:14:13,727 --> 00:14:15,604
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生…

250
00:14:16,689 --> 00:14:19,900
<font color="japanese">うぐぐぐ… うう うわ…

251
00:14:19,984 --> 00:14:20,860
<font color="japanese">ガ… ガハッ…

252
00:14:20,943 --> 00:14:21,735
<font color="japanese">あっ！

253
00:14:21,819 --> 00:14:22,862
<font color="japanese">うっ　うあああ…

254
00:14:22,945 --> 00:14:24,738
<font color="japanese">マズい！ 二次変質だ

255
00:14:24,864 --> 00:14:25,614
<font color="japanese">てえっ！

256
00:14:25,698 --> 00:14:28,367
<font color="japanese">うっ… ううう… ううっ

257
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:33,789
<font color="japanese">さ… さ… き… 先生～！

258
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:37,126
<font color="japanese"><i>ウガァァァ</i>

259
00:14:41,171 --> 00:14:42,965
<font color="japanese"><i>ウオォォ…</i>

260
00:14:47,970 --> 00:14:49,054
<font color="japanese">うう…

261
00:14:49,555 --> 00:14:51,348
<font color="japanese">ハアッ… ハァ…

262
00:14:51,432 --> 00:14:52,725
<font color="japanese">クソッ

263
00:14:52,808 --> 00:14:53,684
<font color="japanese">奴を追うぞ！

264
00:14:53,767 --> 00:14:54,393
<font color="japanese">ああ！

265
00:15:01,483 --> 00:15:05,029
<font color="japanese">ああ…
<font color="japanese">どうしてこんなことに…

266
00:15:05,946 --> 00:15:07,114
<font color="japanese">はあ…

267
00:15:08,407 --> 00:15:08,908
<font color="japanese">えっ？

268
00:15:11,493 --> 00:15:15,164
<font color="japanese">はっ… ああ… はああ…

269
00:15:15,247 --> 00:15:17,333
<font color="japanese"><i>ウウウ…</i>

270
00:15:20,878 --> 00:15:23,797
<font color="japanese"><i>ウオォォ…</i>

271
00:15:23,881 --> 00:15:26,300
<font color="japanese">か… 加賀くん！

272
00:15:27,343 --> 00:15:29,678
<font color="japanese"><i>ウガアア！</i>

273
00:15:30,471 --> 00:15:31,180
<font color="japanese">いたぞ！

274
00:15:31,972 --> 00:15:35,601
<font color="japanese"><i>ウワアアー</i>

275
00:15:35,851 --> 00:15:36,852
<font color="japanese">あっ！

276
00:15:37,353 --> 00:15:38,896
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生！

277
00:15:38,979 --> 00:15:41,857
<font color="japanese">あ… これでは
<font color="japanese">うかつに手は出せないぞ

278
00:15:41,941 --> 00:15:45,235
<font color="japanese">そいつはデイモン･ホールを
<font color="japanese">発症した加賀だ

279
00:15:45,736 --> 00:15:48,113
<font color="japanese">佐々木結衣に
<font color="japanese">危害を加える気配がない

280
00:15:48,948 --> 00:15:51,158
<font color="japanese">一体 どうするつもりなんだ

281
00:15:51,992 --> 00:15:55,746
<font color="japanese">もしかしたら
<font color="japanese">好きなのかもしれないな

282
00:15:55,829 --> 00:15:57,122
<font color="japanese">佐々木結衣のことを

283
00:15:57,206 --> 00:15:59,500
<font color="japanese">す 好きだと？

284
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:02,628
<font color="japanese">彼女に対する
<font color="japanese">加賀の従順さを見ただろ

285
00:16:03,671 --> 00:16:06,256
<font color="japanese">少年の時から
<font color="japanese">ずっと一緒だったんだ

286
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:09,635
<font color="japanese">ひそかに憧れていたとしても
<font color="japanese">不思議ではない

287
00:16:09,718 --> 00:16:13,681
<font color="japanese">理性を失って 感情が
<font color="japanese">むき出しになったってことか

288
00:16:13,764 --> 00:16:14,640
<font color="japanese">う う…

289
00:16:14,723 --> 00:16:16,767
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生を返して！

290
00:16:16,850 --> 00:16:17,643
<font color="japanese">久子！

291
00:16:18,102 --> 00:16:18,644
<font color="japanese"><i>グワッ！</i>

292
00:16:19,144 --> 00:16:19,645
<font color="japanese">ハッ！

293
00:16:19,728 --> 00:16:20,312
<font color="japanese"><i>グワオ！</i>

294
00:16:20,396 --> 00:16:21,563
<font color="japanese">きゃっ！

295
00:16:22,398 --> 00:16:22,982
<font color="japanese">久子！

296
00:16:23,065 --> 00:16:23,565
<font color="japanese">うっ！

297
00:16:23,649 --> 00:16:24,149
<font color="japanese">あっ…

298
00:16:24,233 --> 00:16:24,733
<font color="japanese">あっ…

299
00:16:24,817 --> 00:16:25,317
<font color="japanese">グッ…

300
00:16:25,401 --> 00:16:28,112
<font color="japanese">あっ… ああ…
<font color="japanese">あっ… はああ…

301
00:16:28,195 --> 00:16:30,990
<font color="japanese"><i>ウウウ…</i>

302
00:16:31,073 --> 00:16:32,282
<font color="japanese">や… やめて

303
00:16:32,366 --> 00:16:33,325
<font color="japanese"><i>ウ…？</i>

304
00:16:35,869 --> 00:16:38,372
<font color="japanese">加賀くん… やめて

305
00:16:39,498 --> 00:16:41,375
<font color="japanese"><i>ウウ… ウウッ…</i>

306
00:16:43,043 --> 00:16:44,378
<font color="japanese">お願い！

307
00:16:44,461 --> 00:16:46,797
<font color="japanese"><i>ウグ… ウグウ…</i>

308
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:49,383
<font color="japanese"><i>グワアア！</i>

309
00:17:04,606 --> 00:17:06,734
<font color="japanese">正気に戻ったのか？

310
00:17:06,817 --> 00:17:08,694
<font color="japanese">いや 油断するな

311
00:17:10,738 --> 00:17:11,864
<font color="japanese"><i>グウウウッ</i>

312
00:17:11,947 --> 00:17:12,656
<font color="japanese">あっ！

313
00:17:15,242 --> 00:17:17,619
<font color="japanese"><i>ウガァー！</i>

314
00:17:18,245 --> 00:17:19,121
<font color="japanese">ぐわっ！

315
00:17:19,204 --> 00:17:20,622
<font color="japanese">きゃああ

316
00:17:22,082 --> 00:17:23,083
<font color="japanese">うわあっ

317
00:17:23,834 --> 00:17:24,710
<font color="japanese">ううっ！

318
00:17:26,170 --> 00:17:27,796
<font color="japanese">ウウウ…

319
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:29,173
<font color="japanese">クソッ！

320
00:17:29,256 --> 00:17:30,174
<font color="japanese">ウウッ！

321
00:17:33,552 --> 00:17:34,386
<font color="japanese">ウルヴァリン！

322
00:17:34,470 --> 00:17:35,220
<font color="japanese">ウワアッ！

323
00:17:35,304 --> 00:17:37,389
<font color="japanese"><i>グオッ… ウウ</i>

324
00:17:37,473 --> 00:17:38,557
<font color="japanese"><i>グッ　オウ！</i>

325
00:17:39,266 --> 00:17:40,017
<font color="japanese">エエッ

326
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:41,977
<font color="japanese">大丈夫？ ウルヴァリン！

327
00:17:42,061 --> 00:17:42,811
<font color="japanese">ああっ！

328
00:17:43,395 --> 00:17:44,813
<font color="japanese">クッウウウ…

329
00:17:46,273 --> 00:17:47,733
<font color="japanese">はあ…

330
00:17:47,816 --> 00:17:48,317
<font color="japanese">あっ？

331
00:17:51,862 --> 00:17:52,863
<font color="japanese">これは？

332
00:17:57,576 --> 00:17:58,577
<font color="japanese"><i>ウウウッ！</i>

333
00:17:59,453 --> 00:18:00,496
<font color="japanese">ウッ！

334
00:18:00,954 --> 00:18:01,747
<font color="japanese">ぐ…

335
00:18:01,830 --> 00:18:04,750
<font color="japanese">うぐぐ…

336
00:18:05,667 --> 00:18:06,251
<font color="japanese">フッ

337
00:18:09,463 --> 00:18:10,005
<font color="japanese">ハアッ！

338
00:18:15,469 --> 00:18:17,304
<font color="japanese">なんて力なの？

339
00:18:17,387 --> 00:18:18,889
<font color="japanese">ビクともしないわ！

340
00:18:19,556 --> 00:18:20,390
<font color="japanese">ウワアッ

341
00:18:20,474 --> 00:18:21,141
<font color="japanese"><i>グワアッ</i>

342
00:18:21,975 --> 00:18:23,018
<font color="japanese">今だ！ 久子

343
00:18:23,602 --> 00:18:24,520
<font color="japanese">はいっ！

344
00:18:26,438 --> 00:18:27,523
<font color="japanese"><i>ウオッ</i>

345
00:18:29,733 --> 00:18:30,609
<font color="japanese">フウッ！

346
00:18:31,944 --> 00:18:35,906
<font color="japanese"><i>グワァァァー</i>

347
00:18:44,498 --> 00:18:45,749
<font color="japanese">やったわ！

348
00:18:45,833 --> 00:18:47,876
<font color="japanese">やっと
<font color="japanese">おねんねしたようだな

349
00:18:48,585 --> 00:18:49,503
<font color="japanese">はあ…

350
00:18:50,879 --> 00:18:51,380
<font color="japanese">あっ

351
00:18:56,552 --> 00:18:57,636
<font color="japanese">はあっ！

352
00:19:05,853 --> 00:19:07,062
<font color="japanese">真田…

353
00:19:07,729 --> 00:19:08,647
<font color="japanese">純！

354
00:19:09,731 --> 00:19:12,192
<font color="japanese">サイクロプス 大丈夫か？

355
00:19:13,026 --> 00:19:14,820
<font color="japanese">いいとこなしだったな

356
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:16,196
<font color="japanese">ああ

357
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:19,658
<font color="japanese">加賀の変質は治まったようだ

358
00:19:19,741 --> 00:19:21,660
<font color="japanese">彼にも早くワクチンを

359
00:19:23,996 --> 00:19:25,164
<font color="japanese">見ろよ

360
00:19:25,664 --> 00:19:27,666
<font color="japanese">涙を流してやがる

361
00:19:31,003 --> 00:19:33,672
<font color="japanese">はっ… はあ… は…

362
00:19:34,715 --> 00:19:36,049
<font color="japanese">はあ…

363
00:19:36,550 --> 00:19:38,594
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生

364
00:19:41,263 --> 00:19:43,807
<font color="japanese">どうして加賀くんまでが…

365
00:19:43,891 --> 00:19:45,893
<font color="japanese">ワクチンを打っておいたが

366
00:19:45,976 --> 00:19:50,564
<font color="japanese">韮崎理子と同じように
<font color="japanese">左上腕に注射の痕があった

367
00:19:51,106 --> 00:19:53,942
<font color="japanese">あれも点滴の痕なのかね？

368
00:19:54,026 --> 00:19:54,860
<font color="japanese">はっ…

369
00:19:57,571 --> 00:19:59,406
<font color="japanese">もう１人の研究員にも

370
00:19:59,489 --> 00:20:01,575
<font color="japanese">ワクチンを
<font color="japanese">打っておきたいんだが

371
00:20:02,201 --> 00:20:03,493
<font color="japanese">純くん？

372
00:20:04,369 --> 00:20:05,787
<font color="japanese">後で呼んでくるわ

373
00:20:08,707 --> 00:20:10,250
<font color="japanese">これを見てくれ

374
00:20:10,334 --> 00:20:11,919
<font color="japanese">何かの原液らしい

375
00:20:12,002 --> 00:20:16,715
<font color="japanese">冷蔵庫にこれと同じ物が
<font color="japanese">大量にあったぜ

376
00:20:16,798 --> 00:20:17,466
<font color="japanese">はっ！

377
00:20:21,011 --> 00:20:23,222
<font color="japanese">はっ… あ… ああ

378
00:20:24,556 --> 00:20:25,974
<font color="japanese">佐々木先生

379
00:20:30,979 --> 00:20:33,732
<font color="japanese">さあ 説明してもらおうか

380
00:20:35,359 --> 00:20:36,443
<font color="japanese">はあ

381
00:20:47,287 --> 00:20:49,539
<font color="japanese"><i>東北上空に入ります</i>

382
00:20:49,623 --> 00:20:52,000
<font color="japanese"><i>着陸地点を指定してください</i>

383
00:21:05,931 --> 00:21:06,765
<font color="japanese">んっ？

384
00:21:08,350 --> 00:21:09,935
<font color="japanese">何だ　これは？

385
00:21:10,769 --> 00:21:13,981
<font color="japanese">意識の中に異質なものが
<font color="japanese">流れ込んでいる

386
00:21:14,856 --> 00:21:17,526
<font color="japanese">これではＸ-ＭＥＮの
